maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: ... Salut !

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: Spheromancer Lea! There you are!
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Spheromanceuse Lea ! Te voilà !

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: It looks like the Spheromancers are leading the race as of now!
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: On dirait que les Spheromanceurs mènent la course en ce moment !

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: Let's continue before that Pentafist catches up-
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Continuons avant que cette Pentafist finisse par nous-

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: Oh! Another shared outdoor area?
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Oh ! Encore un extérieur partagé ?

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: And I'm last, aren't I?
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Et je suis dernière, c'est ça ?

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: Indeed! We Spheromancers are at the very front, as expected!
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Effectivement ! Nous, les Spheromanceurs, sommes les premiers, comme l'on pouvait s'y attendre !

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: Oui, oui, just keep your smug face while it lasts.
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Oui, oui, continue avec ta fierté tant qu'elle dure.

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: The race isn't over yet!
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: La course n'est pas finie !
... Salut...

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: Spheromancer Lea! There you are!
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Spheromanceuse Lea ! Te voilà !

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: I just got here myself. Grasshead has been waiting.
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Je viens juste d'arriver moi-même. Monsieur Tête-d'Herbe nous attendait déjà.

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: Indeed.
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Effectivement.

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: Still I'm saddened to see a Spheromancer overtaken by a mere Pentafist.
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Mais bon, je suis triste de voir un Spheromanceur se faire doubler par une simple Pentafist.

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: Well, the race isn't over yet.
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Oui, bon, la course n'est pas encore terminée.

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: Who knows, maybe this Pentafist Scrub will end up overtaking you as well!
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Qui sait, peut-être que cette Pentafist amateur va finir par te dépasser toi aussi !

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: Anyway, we all just crossed blades with the Son of the East.
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: En tout cas, nous venons de croiser le fer avec le Fils de l'Est.

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: Still think it's just a funny ape, Pentafist?
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Tu penses toujours que c'est un singe marrant, Pentafist ?

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: That battle was quite intense, non?
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Ce combat était assez intense, non ?

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: Apes are still funny, though! That will never change!
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Mais les singes sont toujours marrants ! Et ils le resteront à jamais !

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: Now, let's race on!!
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Continuons la course !!

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: Told you, right? Great view!
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Je te l'avais dit, non ? C'est une belle vue !

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: You can barely see anything through the leaves...
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Tu peux à peine voir quelque chose à travers les feuilles...

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: Come on, let's continue with the temple.
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Allez, continuons le temple.

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: Why the rush?
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Pourquoi se presser ?

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: Hi!
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Salut !

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: Countless leaves.
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Des feuilles innombrables.

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: Bundled together.
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Regroupées ensembles.

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: Like green clouds, up in the sky.
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Comme des nuages verts, haut dans le ciel.

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: [nods]
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: [acquiesce]

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: There are...\. too many of them...\. and too little space...
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Il y en a...\. trop...\. et pas assez de place...

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: Don't give up, pal! I know you can do it!
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: N'abandonne pas, mec ! Je sais que tu peux le faire !

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: And once I thought they were cute...
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Et moi qui pensais qu'ils étaient mignons...

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: I knew it! Once I saw this giant tree, I knew this was gonna happen!
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Je le savais ! Une fois que j'ai vu cet arbre géant, je savais que ça arriverait !

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: Of course they'd make us climb it up and walk on those narrow branches!!
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Bien entendu, il fallait qu'il nous fasse grimper dessus et marcher sur ces branches étroites !!

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: Those stupid game designers with their stupid heights!!
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Ces stupides concepteurs de jeu avec leurs satanées hauteurs !!

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: Now, now there...
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Bon... aller... aller...

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: Sergiy
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Sergiy

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: Really now...
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Non mais vraiment...

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: A laughing monkey flying on a cloud?
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Un singe qui se marre et qui vole sur un nuage ?

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: This is ridiculous, don't you agree?
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: C'est ridicule, tu trouves pas ?

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: [nods]
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: [acquiesce]

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: Right? What were developers thinking!
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Hein ? Ils pensaient à quoi ces développeurs ?

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: [shakes head]
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: [secoue la tête]

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: Hmm, then it must be just me.
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Hmm, alors ça doit être juste moi.

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: [yes]
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: [oui]

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: [no]
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: [non]

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: Honestly, these boss fights are getting a tiny bit too crazy for my taste.
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: Honnêtement, ces combats de boss deviennent un peu trop cinglés à mon goût.

maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.orig: What next?\. Will the ape surf on a hover board or something?
maps/tree-dng/f3/branch-middle.json/enti.text: C'est quoi la suite ?\. Le singe va surfer sur un Hoverboard ou quoi ?

maps/tree-dng/f4/boss.json/entities/16/s.orig: One has reached the very top of Grand Krys'kajo.
maps/tree-dng/f4/boss.json/entities/16/s.text: Il a atteint la cime du Grand Krys'kajo.

maps/tree-dng/f4/boss.json/entities/16/s.orig: Standing high above the earth, one is now ready.
maps/tree-dng/f4/boss.json/entities/16/s.text: Tout en hauteur de la terre ferme, il est maintenant prêt.

maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.orig: \i[arrow-n] Up
maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.text: \i[arrow-n] En haut

maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.orig: Another strange visitor has arrived at the roots.
maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.text: Un autre visiteur étrange est arrivé aux racines.

maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.orig: One trying to reach the top of Krys'kajo as well?
maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.text: Encore un qui cherche à atteindre la cime du Krys'kajo ?

maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.orig: One needs to prove the mastery of \c[3]Shock\c[0] and \c[3]Wave\c[0] for one to ascend.
maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.text: Il doit prouver sa maitrise du \c[3]Choc\c[0] et de l'\c[3]Onde\c[0] pour pouvoir grimper.

maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.orig: I shall watch this one closely.
maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.text: Je dois garder un œil sur lui.

maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.orig: Ape Guy!! Did you meet the ape guy?
maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.text: L'homme singe !! Est-ce que vous avez rencontré l'homme singe ?

maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.orig: [nods]
maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.text: [acquiesce]

maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.orig: Yes, I did.
maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.text: Oui, je l'ai rencontré.

maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.orig: Also, what is this? Wasn't this supposed to be a race?
maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.text: Et sinon, c'est quoi ça ? Ce n'était pas censé être une course ?

maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.orig: You bet it is!
maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.text: Bien sûr que si !

maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.orig: Then why the D-Link?
maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.text: Alors pourquoi le D-Link ?

maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.orig: Why not? It doesn't hurt to have a few breaks in between.
maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.text: Pourquoi pas ? Ça ne peut pas faire de mal de faire une pause de temps en temps.

maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.orig: We just started moments ago!
maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.text: On vient juste de commencer !

maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.orig: Oui, but I had to talk about the ape!
maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.text: Oui, mais il fallait que je parle du singe !

maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.orig: Apes are so funny!
maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.text: Les singes sont trop marrants !

maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.orig: Funny?
maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.text: Marrants ?

maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.orig: This ape oversees every Seeker that enters this place.
maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.text: Ce singe surveille tous les \v[lore.title.seeker]s qui entrent dans cet endroit.

maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.orig: It's a mysterious yet honorable creature of ancient origin.
maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.text: C'est une mystérieuse mais honorable créature de l'ancien temps.

maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.orig: So? I still think it's funny!
maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.text: Et ? Je pense toujours qu'il est drôle !

maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.orig: Fine, then. Let's properly start the race, already.
maps/tree-dng/g/center-02-connect.json/e.text: Comme tu veux. Maintenant on pourrait enfin commencer la course.
